  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">Mechanism | Add Mechanism (Editor)</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Heading4 Toggle_atocs_">What is a Mechanism?</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">A <text styleclass="VariableName-IT">Mechanism</text>, in the context of <text styleclass="T_Menu">Add Mechanism</text>, is a <text styleclass="Interface">Mechanism-Editor</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> and </text><text styleclass="Interface">tab</text><text styleclass="Body Text">.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">Use <text styleclass="Interface">Mechanism-Editors</text> to add <text styleclass="Element">Parts</text>, <text styleclass="Element">Joints</text>, <text styleclass="Element">Cams</text>, <text styleclass="Element">Gears</text>, <text styleclass="Element">Belts</text>, ... to design your machine. </para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;"/></para>
    <para styleclass="VariableName" style="text-indent:-18px; margin-left:21px;">IMPORTANT: Gravitational Force Vector is normal the TOP Plane</para>
    <para styleclass="VariableName" style="text-indent:-18px; margin-left:21px;"><table styleclass="PopupTable2" rowcount="1" colcount="1" style="cell-padding:0px;">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Body Table">The <text styleclass="Interface2">Gravity Vector</text> is in the negative Y-axis direction of the <text styleclass="Interface">Front-View</text><text styleclass="Interface2">(f3)</text> in the <text styleclass="Interface">Model-Editor</text>.</para>
          <para styleclass="Body Table">Before you add the <text styleclass="VariableName" style="color:#ff0000;">first</text> <text styleclass="Interface">Mechanism-Editor</text>, to a <text styleclass="Element">Plane</text>, consider the type of machine. </para>
          <para styleclass="Body Table">For example, if your machine has a horizontal indexing or rotating table, add the <text styleclass="Interface">Mechanism-Editor</text> for the table to the <text styleclass="Interface2">Top</text><text styleclass="Element"> Plane</text><text styleclass="Body Text">, or a </text><text styleclass="Element">Plane</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> that is parallel to the </text><text styleclass="Interface2">Top</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> </text><text styleclass="Element">Plane</text><text styleclass="Body Text">.</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;"/></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading3_atocs_">Add Mechanism-Editor</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><table styleclass="Standard" rowcount="5" colcount="2" style="width:auto;">
      <tr style="vertical-align:middle">
